<div class=" os-hasSolution " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp225643904">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp4814048"><a class="os-number" href="chapter-21#fs-idp225643904-solution">15</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-problem-container">
