<p id="fs-idm43346352">(a) emission of a β particle</p>
<p id="fs-idp177484800">(b) emission of a β<sup>+</sup> particle</p>
<p id="fs-idp122950864">(c) capture of an electron</p>
</div></div>

</div>
<div class=" " data-type="exercise" id="fs-idm39924368">
